translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 中々バラエティに富んだ結果やね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's quite a varied set of results."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やはり意外なのは四天王全員の敗北でしょうか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Perhaps the most surprising thing is that all four of the Heavenly Kings were defeated."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これには会場も動揺が隠せない様子でした」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Even the audience couldn't hide their shock over this."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「話によれば四天王が弱なったわけちゃうらしいし、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "From what I've heard, it's not that the Heavenly Kings have gotten any weaker,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 四天王の敗退が今大会のレベルの高さを証明しとるとも言えるね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "but their defeat actually proves how high the level of this tournament really is."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「明後日からの二回戦では、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "From the day after tomorrow, in the second round,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 当然ですが誰もが一回は勝ち上がった猛者ばかりの試合」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "naturally, every match will be between fierce fighters who have all won at least once."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「どのような激闘を見せてくれるか、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Let’s look forward to what kind of fierce battles they will show,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今から期待しちゃいましょう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'm already excited to see it."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それでは明日もこの時間にお会いしましょう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well then, let's meet again at this time tomorrow."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「次の試合自体は明後日や、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The next match itself is the day after tomorrow,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 勘違いしたらあかんで〜」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "so don't get it wrong~"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「この番組は、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "This program is brought to you by,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いつもかわいいモンスターありがとうのキャラ屋、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Chara-ya, who always says thank you to cute monsters,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: の提供でお送りしました」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "sponsoring us today."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、あらら〜……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, oh no..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「長田君、負けちゃったって」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Nagata-kun lost, they say."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「相手がミラクルさんだから
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, since his opponent was Miracle-san,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おかしなことにはなってないだろうけど……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "it probably didn’t turn into something strange, but..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 落ち込んでないかな……大丈夫かな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I wonder if he's feeling down... is he alright..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うっ、うわーーーーーーーん！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Waaahhhhhhh!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「負けちゃったよー！　為す術なかったよー！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I lost! I didn't have a chance!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一撃でノックダウンだよー！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I got knocked down with a single blow!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おーーい、おいおいおい！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hey— hey, hey, hey!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 室内に飛び込んできた長田君が、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nagata-kun rushed into the room,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたの膝でおいおい泣きだした。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and started sobbing on your knee.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あっ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「こないだ、対等でありたいんだとか、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The other day, saying he wanted to be equals,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 対等じゃなきゃ友達じゃねえとか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: that if we weren't equals, we wouldn't be friends..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まーなんか色々と言ったけど……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, he said a lot of things like that..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「本当のダチってそんなこと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But true friends don't care about that kind of stuff!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 気にするようなもんじゃねぇよな！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's not something you should worry about!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ってわけでこれからもよろしくな！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "So, from now on, let's keep it up!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 相棒！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Partner!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 親指をグッと突き出す長田君は
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nagata-kun gave a strong thumbs-up,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とっても調子が良かった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and was feeling really upbeat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうだね、一緒に＜エール＞ちゃんの
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's right, let's work hard together to support 'Eiru-chan.'"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サポートがんばろーね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "We'll do our best to support her."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そっすね、そっすね！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Yeah, right, yeah!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こうして長田君があなたの隣に戻ってきた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And so, Nagata-kun returned to your side.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた達三人は、改めてホットミルクを飲みながら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The three of you once again drank hot milk together,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作戦会議を始めた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and began a strategy meeting.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いいか、＜エール＞。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Listen, 'Eiru.'"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺が見る限りこの闘神大会、強敵ばかりだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "From what I can see, this Martial God Tournament is full of formidable opponents."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だがなぁ、へへっ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But, heh heh,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺がいれば楽勝だ、任せとけよな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "if I'm here, it'll be an easy win. Leave it to me."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 長田君はどこまでも調子が良かった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nagata-kun was in high spirits no matter what.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そして、この俺が見る限り！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "And from what I see!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やっぱりアームズさんは強敵だな！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Arms-san is definitely a tough opponent!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうだねー、このままだときっとアームズさんと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Yeah, if things keep going this way, we're surely going to face Arms-san,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦うことになるねー、ふうふう、ずず……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "We'll have to fight him, whew whew, sssip..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「でも、その前に次の対戦相手さんも重要だけどね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But before that, our next opponent is important too."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「よっし、＜エール＞！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Alright, 'Eiru!'"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 明日は修行は中止！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "No training tomorrow!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 街に出て情報収集と行こうぜ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Let's head out into town and gather information!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おーっ」
リセットと長田君は仲良く腕を天に突き上げた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset and Nagata-kun happily raised their arms toward the sky.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた達は情報収集をする為に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You all went out to gather information,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Perhaps the most surprising thing is that all four of the Heavenly Kings were defeated."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Even the audience couldn't hide their shock over this."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「話によれば四天王が弱なったわけちゃうらしいし、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "From what I've heard, it's not that the Heavenly Kings have gotten any weaker,"

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "but their defeat actually proves how high the level of this tournament really is."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'm already excited to see it."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それでは明日もこの時間にお会いしましょう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well then, let's meet again at this time tomorrow."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The next match itself is the day after tomorrow,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「負けちゃったよー！　為す術なかったよー！

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I got knocked down with a single blow!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おーーい、おいおいおい！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hey— hey, hey, hey!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 室内に飛び込んできた長田君が、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nagata-kun rushed into the room,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたの膝でおいおい泣きだした。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and started sobbing on your knee.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あっ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「こないだ、対等でありたいんだとか、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The other day, saying he wanted to be equals,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 対等じゃなきゃ友達じゃねえとか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: that if we weren't equals, we wouldn't be friends..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まーなんか色々と言ったけど……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, he said a lot of things like that..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「本当のダチってそんなこと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But true friends don't care about that kind of stuff!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 気にするようなもんじゃねぇよな！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's not something you should worry about!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ってわけでこれからもよろしくな！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "So, from now on, let's keep it up!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 相棒！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Partner!"

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nagata-kun gave a strong thumbs-up,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and was feeling really upbeat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サポートがんばろーね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "We'll do our best to support her."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そっすね、そっすね！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Yeah, right, yeah!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こうして長田君があなたの隣に戻ってきた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And so, Nagata-kun returned to your side.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた達三人は、改めてホットミルクを飲みながら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The three of you once again drank hot milk together,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作戦会議を始めた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and began a strategy meeting.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いいか、＜エール＞。

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But, heh heh,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 長田君はどこまでも調子が良かった。
